author: gstein
msg: Add comparison functions to the State object.
* subversion/tests/cmdline/svntest/wc.py:
(State.normalize): new method to create a "normalized" form of the State
instance.
(State.compare): new method to compare two State objects
(State.compare_and_display): new method to compare two State objects and
generate output similar to the old tree.compare_trees() function.
(State.old_tree): shift all the nodelist construction logic off to
StateItem.as_node_tuple() and then use it.
(State.__eq__): normalize the State instances before trying to compare
their innards.
(StateItem.as_node_tuple): new method to return an old-style tuple for a
"nodelist" for turning into an old-style tree.
(item_to_node): interim helper function for the display code
(display_nodes): copied from tree.compare_trees() and tweaked a bit for
our new usage.
(default_singleton_handler): copied from tree.py and tweaked a bit.
